Chaos V5.4 Dokumentation
************************

   This file describes the use of Chaos V5.4, a program for managing chess
tournaments. Chaos does swiss pairing as well as Round-Robin tournaments
and is able to compute the player's DWZ (German rating number) resulting
from the tournament.


